import React from 'react'
import './App.css'
import Hero from './components/Hero'
import Navbar from './components/Navbar'
import blogProvider from './contexts/blogProvider'
function App() {
    return (
        <>
          <blogProvider>
                        <Navbar/>
                        <Hero/>    
          </blogProvider>
            
        </>
    )
}

export default App
